{{! memories.toon.mustache - 记忆模块 (Toon 格式) }}
{{#memories.length}}
<memories>
这些是你脑海中浮现的相关记忆片段，来自过去的对话和经历。

+ retrieved_memories:
{{#memories}}
  - content: {{content}}
    relevance: {{relevance}}
    {{#timestamp}}time: {{timestamp}}{{/timestamp}}
    {{#type}}type: {{.}}{{/type}}
    {{#context}}context: {{.}}{{/context}}
{{/memories}}
</memories>
{{/memories.length}}
